SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[CheckInDate], [r].[CheckOutDate], [r].[CreatedBy], [r].[CreatedDate], [r].[GuestId], [r].[RoomId], [r].[UpdatedBy], [r].[UpdatedDate], [g].[Id], [g].[Country], [g].[CreatedBy], [g].[CreatedDate], [g].[DateOfBirth], [g].[Email], [g].[EmergencyContact], [g].[FirstName], [g].[LastName], [g].[Phone], [g].[SpecialRequests], [g].[UpdatedBy], [g].[UpdatedDate], [r0].[Id], [r0].[CreatedBy], [r0].[CreatedDate], [r0].[Price], [r0].[RoomNumber], [r0].[RoomType], [r0].[Status], [r0].[UpdatedBy], [r0].[UpdatedDate]
